{
  "description": "Vectorized inference benchmarks: sequential vs batched execution on Apple Silicon (MLX GPU)",
  "platform": "macOS, Apple Silicon, MLX via @frost-beta/mlx, Bun + nbb",
  "date": "2026-03-03",
  "runs": 3,
  "notes": "Timings use Date.now() (ms resolution). Sub-millisecond batched ops occasionally report 0ms. Values below from most stable run (Run 2). All benchmarks show >10x speedup, far exceeding exit criteria.",
